I'm done.

78
00:04:50,823 --> 00:04:52,552
我要走了，安妮
I'm leaving, Annie.

79
00:04:54,294 --> 00:04:56,319
我要回芝加哥去了
I'm going back to Chicago.

80
00:04:57,230 --> 00:04:58,788
