唯一一份现存的证据
The sole surviving record
of an uncharted island.

135
00:08:15,828 --> 00:08:18,888
一个被认为只在神话里存在的地方
A place that was
thought to exist
only in myth.

136
00:08:19,198 --> 00:08:20,222
